毀QB係戰術黎架喎<br />\n泥門核心就係蛭魔 咁緊係收佢皮啦<br />\n同埋峨王真係跟規矩去打比賽<br />\n進攻停止就真係停 唔會抽水<br />\n你最多話佢地戰術嘔心同仆街<br />\n但on9就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876c8bd24b6bbedda3daaf14f032b10db81b037b","tid":394494,"uid":51172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我D 心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOP1 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/L01k_S5TxPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL01k_S5TxPY&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bf311aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L01k_S5TxPY</a><br />\nOP3 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/xVYktOB4K1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxVYktOB4K1M&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8d6edf37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xVYktOB4K1M</a><br />\nOP4 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/VoftWzc6Cto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVoftWzc6Cto&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=98329498\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VoftWzc6Cto</a><br />\nED1 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/jA_Oi5duNTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjA_Oi5duNTQ&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=875a7638\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jA_Oi5duNTQ</a><br />\nED2 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/RylK78Bvpxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRylK78Bvpxo&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=964d240d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RylK78Bvpxo</a><br />\nED3 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zTd6RPmWJGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzTd6RPmWJGk&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e0ac652d\" target=\"_blank\">